articles.title: Americans hungry for weight-loss drugs grapple with supply and insurance hurdles - Reuters
articles.description: Americans are still eagerly seeking prescriptions for Eli Lilly and Novo Nordisk's weight-loss and diabetes drugs but cannot always fill them because of supply issues and insurance hurdles, according to their doctors.
